86
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,900
Vi må af sted.

87
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:32,500
Farvel, Mr Turner.

88
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,100
Følg med!

89
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:39,200
Farvel...

90
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,100
Elizabeth.

91
00:10:14,100 --> 00:10:16,100
Tøv en kende!

92
